item.title: Discord bot for xkcd
item.description: Background xkcd XKCD is a webcomic by Randall Munroe. It consists primarily of romance, sarcasm, math, and language, appealing to a lot of nerdy people (and some non-nerds too). I really enjoy it, and felt the need to create a discord bot for it. Discord Quote from their website as of today: All-in-one voice and text chat for gamers that’s free, secure, and works on both your desktop and phone.
